{"tid":2040060,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"RTHK今晚直播訪問蛋撻の達人彭定康","createTime":"2020-05-28T10:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T12:50:01.000Z","uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2127458901956202fd0d141e7d6e72442670f5a7","tid":2040060,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/05/28/F782Dg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F05%2F28%2FF782Dg.png&h=ce790369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHK.Pulse/photos/a.193038527405873/3123891714320525/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHK.Pulse%2Fphotos%2Fa.193038527405873%2F3123891714320525%2F&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=a2ece01c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHK.Pulse/photos/a.193038527405873/3123891714320525/</a><br />\n<br />\nRTHK's The Pulse<br />\nPage Liked &middot; 56 mins &middot;<br />\n<br />\n[TONIGHT: Live discussion on the National Security Law]<br />\n<br />\nThe National People&rsquo;s Congress is deliberating a draft decision to formulate the &ldquo;HK National Security Law&rdquo;. The law is designed to penalise acts of secession and subversion of state power, terrorist acts, and foreign intervention.<br />\n<br />\nWith us to talk about the impact of this law on Hong Kong is former governor Chris Patten.<br />\n<br />\nTomorrow, when the law is expected to be put to a vote by the NPC Standing Committee, we will also be talking to Exco member Ronny Tong.<br />\n<br />\n#nationalsecuritylaw #Basiclaw #hongkong"},{"pid":"540807e3e88ab4cf5679f8e1f51c0a50935516be","tid":2040060,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRcUoav.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRc